## 6. Update `UserService`

```java
private final PersonPointOfSalesRelationshipRepository relationshipRepository;
private final PointOfSalesRepository pointOfSalesRepository;
```

Inside `mapToResponse()`:

```java
List<SalesPointResponse> salesPoints =
        relationshipRepository.findByPersonUserId(user.getUserId())
                .stream()
                .map(rel -> {
                    PointOfSalesEntity pos = pointOfSalesRepository
                            .findByPointOfSalesId(rel.getPointOfSalesId())
                            .orElseThrow();

                    return new SalesPointResponse(
                            pos.getPointOfSalesId(),
                            pos.getLabel(),
                            rel.getOrgUnitId(),
                            rel.getRelationshipType()
                    );
                })
                .toList();

response.setSalesPoints(salesPoints);
```

